author: Cleo Abram
description:
This device can remove blood clots in a new way...it’s called the “millispinner” and it’s tiny.

Scientists are hoping it’ll be a more effective way of removing blood clots. Here's how it works...

For more optimistic science and tech stories, subscribe!
